quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,135,"Era (abayudaaya n'abakurisitaayo) baagamba nti; mubeere bayudaaya oba bakurisitaayo lwemunaaluηηama. Bagambe (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti; nedda tujja kugoberera ddiini ya Ibrahim eragira okusinza Katonda omu yekka, era (Ibrahim) tabangako mubagatta kintu kirala ku Katonda"
  2,136,"(Mwe abasiraamu) mugambe nti; tukkiriza Katonda, n'ebyassibwa gyetuli, n'ebyassibwa ku Ibrahim, ne Ismail, ne Ishaak, ne Yakuubu n'eri bazzukulu baabwe. N'ebyo ebyaweebwa Musa ne Issa na byonna ebyaweebwa bannabbi abalala nga biva eri mukama Katonda omulezi waabwe era tetubaawulayawulamu era nga naffe twewaddeyo gyali"
  2,137,"Bwe banakkiririza mu ebyo bye mukkiriza, olwo ban'aba baluηηamye. Naye bwe banaava ku nzikiriza eyo, mazima ddala bo bajja kubeera mu kuwalaaza mpaka. Era nga Katonda ajja kubakukolerako. Era ye (Katonda) awulira, era mumanyi"
  2,138,"(Obusiraamu) y'eddiini Katonda gyayagala munnyikiremu. Ate ani asinga Katonda okunnyikiza, era naffe oyo gwe tusinza"
  2,139,Bagambe (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti; mutuwakanya ku bikwata ku Katonda. Ng'ate Katonda ye mulezi waffe era omulezi wa mmwe. Tukola emirimu gyaffe nga nammwe mukola egyammwe so ng'ate ffe tumusinza mu bumu bwe yekka
  2,140,"Oba mugamba nti; ddala Ibrahim ne Ismail ne Ishaak ne Yakuubu ne bazzukulu baabwe baali bayudaaya oba bakurisitaayo. Bagambe (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti mmwe musinga okumanya, oba Katonda? Ani mubi okusinga akweka obujulizi bwalina obuva eri Katonda? Mukama Katonda bye mukola tabisudde muguluka"
  2,141,"Omulembe ogwo gwayita, era gwagenda n'ebyagwo, nga nammwe bwe mulina ebyammwe bye mukola era temugenda kubuuzibwa ku ebyo bye baakola. E jjuzu"